title: Jump on command
description: Make your dog jump by giving him command. This is short course that will teach your dog to jump better.

title: Attack on command
description: Make your dog attack by giving him command. This is short course that will teach your dog to attack to the end.

title: Roll on command
description:
Make your roll each on command. Caution: Don't overuse because the dog might get concussion
                    and will not react to anything for a couple of minutes.
                    Don't worry, he will be back.
